import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { DetailListHeader } from "./DetailListHeader"
import { Playground, PropsTable } from "docz"

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"detaillistheader"}}>{`DetailListHeader`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"component"}}>{`Component`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"this-component-is-used-as-a-title-for-the-boxlist-folderview-and-checkout-components"}}>{`This component is used as a title for the BoxList, FolderView, and Checkout components`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __code={`<DetailListHeader title={\'Boxes\'} />`} __scope={{props,DetailListHeader}}>
    <DetailListHeader title={"Boxes"} />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"props-interface"}}>{`Props Interface`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={DetailListHeader} /> </MDXTag>
